com.eco.bio7.image.measure

Class Bio7ImageJAnalyse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.eco.bio7.image.measure.Bio7ImageJAnalyse

  • public class Bio7ImageJAnalyse
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides static methods for the access of values as an array from a particle analysis of ImageJ. This class supports the transfer to the R application by means of the Rserve application.
    Author:
    Bio7
